# 🚀 E-Commerce Data Platform - Complete Data Engineering Solution

A **production-ready data engineering platform** built entirely with **AWS Free Tier** services. Complete ETL/ELT pipeline with data lake, Spark processing, and analytics dashboards.

![AWS](https://img.shields.io/badge/AWS-Serverless-orange)
![Spark](https://img.shields.io/badge/Apache-Spark-red)
![Python](https://img.shields.io/badge/Python-3.11-blue)
![Cost](https://img.shields.io/badge/Cost-$0--3%2Fmonth-success)
![License](https://img.shields.io/badge/License-MIT-green)

---

## 📊 Project Overview

Complete data engineering demonstration featuring:

✅ **Medallion Architecture** (Bronze/Silver/Gold)  
✅ **Real-time + Batch Processing** (Spark + Lambda)  
✅ **Automated Data Quality** (Great Expectations)  
✅ **Serverless Orchestration** (Step Functions)  
✅ **Data Warehouse** (Star Schema Design)  
✅ **BI Dashboards** (QuickSight)  
✅ **100% Free Tier** (or $0-3/month)  

