## 🛠️ AWS Services Used (All FREE Tier)

| Service | Purpose | Free Tier | Cost/Month |
|---------|---------|-----------|-----------|
| **S3** | Data Lake (Bronze/Silver/Gold) | 5GB | $0 ✅ |
| **Lambda** | Data ingestion, quality checks | 1M requests | $0 ✅ |
| **EMR Serverless** | Spark ETL jobs | 400 vCPU-hours | $0 ✅ |
| **Glue** | Crawlers & Data Catalog | 1M objects | $0 ✅ |
| **Step Functions** | Orchestration | 4k transitions | $0 ✅ |
| **DynamoDB** | Metadata, watermarks, DQ results | 25GB | $0 ✅ |
| **Athena** | SQL queries on data | 1TB queries | $0 ✅ |
| **EventBridge** | Scheduling | 5M events | $0 ✅ |
| **CloudWatch** | Logs & monitoring | 5GB logs | $0 ✅ |
| **SNS** | Alerting | 1k emails | $0 ✅ |
| **QuickSight** | BI dashboards | 1 user | $0 ✅ |
| **IAM** | Access control | Unlimited | $0 ✅ |

**Total: $0-3/month** (after free tier ends)

