## 🔐 Security Considerations

- ✅ All data encrypted at rest (S3, DynamoDB)
- ✅ IAM roles with least privilege
- ✅ VPC for EMR Serverless
- ✅ No hardcoded credentials
- ✅ Cloudtrail logging (optional)

**For production:**
- Enable S3 versioning & MFA delete
- Add S3 bucket encryption
- Enable Glue data catalog encryption
- Use AWS KMS for key management
- Add VPC endpoints for private networking

